node.text: We’d like to introduce you all to the newest member of our squad; Pearce London Parkinson. 🖤 He made his debut on Sunday 7/18, weighing a healthy 8lb 6oz. & has the calmest little demeanor, which is truly the missing puzzle piece to our family!🖤 We are SO incredibly grateful to God, for this sweet & healthy baby boy blessing!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by WHITTNEY PARKINSON DESIGN on July 05, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
I love working on older historical homes, not just because of their character but because of their challenge. They are messy, and there are headaches and unknowns. But in the end; THAT is the magic. In my #1920MKtudor project, this beautiful master suite (which wasn’t a thing in the 1920’s), was created by utilizing a flat roof space above the sun room (see last photo). Voila! ✨
📸 @sarahshieldsphoto
